docs.lead_paragraph: RIO DE JANEIRO-- With Carnival here just ended, tourist interests in this Brazilian city are particularly conscious of the need to expand existing facilities for visitors and to provide new ones. At present, there are only two first-class hotels in the popular Flamengo and Copacabana sections of Rio, and the high cost of property is making further hotel investment difficult.
